headline: Consumers Energy Uses Smart Technology to Eliminate Over 72,000 Power Outages This Year
summary: Consumers Energy's investment in smart technology for Michigan's electric grid is paying off, keeping the lights on for over 72,000 customers who would have otherwise lost power at some point this year.
